com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.log

Class Logger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.log.Logger

  • public final class Logger
extends java.lang.Object
    Logger for the Mapbox Maps SDK for Android

    Default implementation relies on Log. Alternative implementations can be set with setLoggerDefinition(LoggerDefinition).
